        "subject": "✅ ARIA Feedback Received - Thank you!",
        "html": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px; max-width: 600px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"color: #4A90E2;\">✅ Thank you for your feedback!</h2>\n  <p>ARIA has recorded your rating of <strong>{{ $('Feedback Processor').item.json.rating }}/5</strong></p>\n  <p>{{ $('Feedback Processor').item.json.message }}</p>\n  <p>Your comments: <em>{{ $('Feedback Processor').item.json.comments }}</em></p>\n  <br>\n  <p>ARIA will use this feedback to improve your next daily briefing.</p>\n  <p><em>— ARIA Feedback System</em></p>\n</div>",
